"Text": "<p><span>We are thrilled to announce a significant leap forward in how we manage our people's experience here at EFG. Say hello to </span><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span>, our new, intuitive, and holistic HR platform, designed with you in mind. Launching this October, </span><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span> is more than just a tool; it's our new digital hub for everything related to your journey with us, created to simplify processes and empower every member of our team. This platform represents our commitment to investing in our people and providing a seamless, modern, and engaging employee experience from day one.</span></p><p><span>For too long, managing HR-related tasks has meant navigating different systems and processes, often leading to confusion and inefficiency. We listened to your feedback and recognized the need for a single source of truth, a centralized platform where everything you need is just a click away. </span><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span> is our answer. It replaces our previous fragmented methods with one unified, user-friendly interface, streamlining everything from tracking goals to requesting time off. This transition is a crucial step in our ongoing effort to build a more connected and efficient workplace for everyone.</span></p><p><span>So, what can you expect from </span><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span>? From </span><span><strong>October 16th</strong></span><span>, you will have access to a personal dashboard that puts all your HR needs at your fingertips. You'll be able to:</span></p><ul><li><span>Seamlessly request and manage annual leave</span></li><li><span>View and download your payslips</span></li><li><span>Update your personal information with ease</span></li><li><span>Explore a dynamic organizational chart to better understand our growing team</span></li></ul><p><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span> also serves as a central place for important company news and documents, ensuring you are always informed and connected to the heart of EFG.</span></p><p><span>In conclusion, the introduction of </span><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span> marks a new chapter in our people management strategy. By embracing this innovative technology, we are not just improving our internal processes; we are fostering a culture of transparency, autonomy, and connection. We are confident that this powerful tool will not only make your daily administrative tasks easier but will also enrich your overall experience as part of the EFG family, giving you more time to focus on what you do best.</span></p><p><span>We invite every member of the EFG community to embrace this exciting change. Between </span><span><strong>October 16th and October 31st</strong></span><span>, take the time to log in to your new </span><span><strong>HiBob</strong></span><span> profile, explore the features, and familiarize yourself with the layout. We encourage you to verify your personal details, check out the </span><span>\"Clubhouse\"</span><span> for company updates, and discover how simple it is to manage your time and attendance. Welcome to a smarter, more connected way of working</span></p>",
